description.en:
"Avalant is a RPG Play and Earn on Avalanche, where players are Ants working in a colony.
AntGold is the primary currency used in Avalant ecosystem.

Join the colony to work, dig, fight, launch quests, expeditions and EARN.
Read the full docs at https://docs.avalant.app"
